    "description": "This carb smart recipe replaces half the white rice for cauliflower rice. Let the oven do the work this time. You'll simmer chicken with tomato and red pepper in a spicy sambal and creamy coconut stock before popping it in the oven to stew. Serve with baked rice and scatter with fresh coriander to finish.",
